   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>The plan for now is to send Django exception emails to a new list called OH-
monitoring-private, or something like that. It will be members-only and you'll 
have to ask me to be on it, but I will try to be as responsive and open as 
possible.

I would be open to suggestions on the list's name! Targeting for 0.11.04.</pre>
   </td>
