  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>The problem:

Right now, when someone hits a bug on the #openhatch site and gets the error page,

The solution:

* Create some Django code that only emails out the stack trace, not the
variables like session ID that might be sensitive.
* Configure the site so it emails them to a public list or otherwise makes them
public. (Bonus points if it drops a note on IRC.)</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
